research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1210:research/history/round_summaries/round_0140.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库；在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 两个小 expert 子库查表 + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 仍判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 320 降到 256，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，在不再削掉第二个 routed expert 的前提下，直接测试“更小 expert 子库 + residual cleanup”能否把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.56x，同时显著优于 r139 的单 expert 失败点并尽量接近 r138 的质量锚点。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1216:research/history/round_summaries/round_0151.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库 local top-k + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，所有库都是静态向量库，不依赖样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不得进入 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r146 仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 40 降到 16，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余训练配方不变，测试在约 0.51x total_cost 下，这条当前最强的兼容三段式结构能否仍明显优于现有 `<0.5x` 区域最佳 FVU=0.1010，从而把高质量锚点向低成本带左移。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1228:research/history/round_summaries/round_0205.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(r(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(r(x))} \u03b3_{e,j}(r(x)) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r(x)=x-\u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i\uff1b{u_i} \u662f\u9759\u6001 shared/coarse \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 routed residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201cshared/coarse \u67e5\u8868 + routed residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u4e0d\u518d\u662f `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` \u7684\u66f4\u77ed\u8def\u5f84\u80fd\u5426\u6210\u7acb\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a r203 \u4e0e r204 \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a\u8fd9\u6761 single-route shared \u7cfb\u5217\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u5e72\u51c0\u5426\u5b9a\uff1b\u76f8\u53cd\uff0cr201 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert K=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4ee5 objective=0.398672\u3001cost=0.210938x\u3001exceed=0.187735 \u6210\u4e3a\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent \u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u70b9\uff0c\u800c r202 \u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u63d0\u5230 192 \u540e exceed \u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u964d\u5230 0.178402\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u8fd9\u6761 family \u7684\u74f6\