research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1517:research/history/round_summaries/round_0124.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线导出仍可直接写成 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + routed expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”流水线，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r121-r123 已经在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的同一低成本子线上连续两轮未形成新前沿，按规则应切 family/切假设；而当前更有信息量的问题是，三段式 `lowrank_expert_residual` 是否还能通过压 trunk 宽度把当前 0.68x 质量锚点进一步左移。相对 r99 仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 40 降到 32，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=112`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接测试在已知强质量配方上，low-rank trunk 是否仍被高估。按现有历史与成本模型推断，这会主要压低 selection cost，并把该点从当前约 0.68x 向更低中成本带回拉，同时仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；如果 FVU 仍能维持在约 0.10 左右，则有机会形成新的中成本 Pareto 段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1625:research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r205-r206 \u5df2\u628a `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5728 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` \u8fd9\u6761 lane \u7684 coarse/cleanup \u5206\u5de5\u57fa\u672c\u6478\u6e05\uff1a`STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` \u867d\u628a objective \u4ece 0.398672 \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u8d8a\u8fc7 r159 \u7684 0.395234\uff0c\u66f4\u6ca1\u6709\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent 0.386114\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8fd9\u6761 family \u4e0a\u505a budget split \u7ec6\u626b\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u4ef7\u503c\u5df2\u7ecf\u660e\u663e\u4e0b\u964d\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1